<p>Each of these shifts can allow you to add more new projects and ideas to your life. Sometimes it can be hard to begin working on something if you ask too much of it.</p>

<p>As an example, I wanted to work on a small tool to block websites. This led me to learn about computer proxies. Which led me to have to learn about computer networking and sockets. Following this trail made what could be perceived as a dull subject (no shade to networking engineers) into an exciting one.</p>

