<h3 id="strategies-to-focus">Strategies to Focus</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Avoid tutorial fallacy: Try to change and add to what you learn.</li>
  <li>Keep a list of ideas: Write down things you think would be cool to build.</li>
  <li>Small is great: Begin with easy projects and build up from there.</li>
  <li>Grow your project step by step: Think about small additions and improvements.</li>
  <li>Share what you make: Talk about your projects with others and get their thoughts.</li>
</ul>

